 peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen you pass by the meadows of Paradise, graze as you like.\u201d I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what are the meadows of Paradise?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThe mosques.\u201d I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32758,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/12\/description-first-at-hawd\/","url_meta":{"origin":11245,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Hawd: Description of first to drink from the Fountain","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 12, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cMy fountain is like the distance between 'Adan and \u2018Amman, cooler than ice, sweeter than honey, its fragrance more pleasant than musk, its cups as numerous as stars in the sky. Whoever drinks from it\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35430,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/03\/27\/jannah-bi-ghayri-hisab\/","url_meta":{"origin":11245,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Tawakkul: Paradise without reckoning, they relied on Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 27, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Imran ibn Husayn reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSeventy thousand from my nation will enter Paradise without reckoning.\u201d They said